## Arquitetura

### Backend
```
Request → Routes → Middleware → Controller → Validator → Service → Repository → Model → PostgreSQL
```

### Frontend
```
Page (SSR) → Client Component → Provider (nuqs + Context) → Hooks (TanStack Query) → API Resource (Axios) → Backend
```

